title: Furby In The SUPRA Ellington
description:
Watch Furby make a half cab flip down a 13-stair look like he's going off a curb. Furby's choice of footwear is the new high performance, mid top Ellington in purple suede and black waxed suede with gold accents, black/gold rope laces, padded purple mesh lining, and it's constructed atop a black SUPRAFOAM midsole that provides the comfort and impact protection SUPRA team riders like Furby demand from their footwear. The black cup sole, with white sidewalls, employs a dual tread that combines herring bone and SUPRA tread for superior traction. 

The Ellington is available at better skate retailers and suprafootwear.com.
